data.description: Located in the hills of City Terrace! This property features 2 bedrooms and 1 bath. Lots of space and potential for updates. Panoramic views of the downtown L.A. skyline and Dodgers Stadium. Stairs leading to the back area. There is a service road in rear of the property. This property is located near California Interstate 10 and 710 freeways.
